title: SMNTY Classics: The FDA's New Rule on Telemedicine Abortion
itunes:title: SMNTY Classics: The FDA's New Rule on Telemedicine Abortion
description:
Good news, what? Recently, the US Food and Drug Administration announced a permanent repeal on the in-person dispensing on a popular medication for abortion. Bridget Todd stops by to explain what that means in this classic episode.
